# Regression: `[]` plus a list pattern with a `...rest` element are
# jointly exhaustive over a list type. Empty covers the zero-length
# case, the rest-binding covers every non-empty length. No wildcard
# arm should be required.

[1 2 3] match
    [] : ,
    [a ...rest] : ,
end

# Same coverage with an explicit prefix in front of the rest-bind.
[1 2 3] match
    [] : ,
    [a b ...rest] : ,
    [a] : ,
end
